<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Redirecionando...</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;}

body{
  background:#ffffff;
  color:#ff5a1f;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  height:100vh;
  text-align:center;
}

/* container */
.container{
  max-width:500px;
  animation:fadeIn 1s ease;
}

/* logo */
.logo{
  font-size:1.6rem;
  font-weight:800;
  color:#ff5a1f;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

/* título */
h1{
  font-size:2.2rem;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* texto */
p{
  color:#cbd5e1;
  margin-bottom:30px;
}

/* loader */
.loader{
  width:50px;
  height:50px;
  border:5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  border-top:5px solid #ff5a1f;
  border-radius:50%;
  animation:spin 1s linear infinite;
  margin:0 auto;
}

/* barra fake progresso */
.progress{
  width:100%;
  height:6px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius:10px;
  margin-top:25px;
  overflow:hidden;
}

.progress-bar{
  height:100%;
  width:0%;
  background:#ff5a1f;
  animation:load 2.5s ease forwards;
}

/* animações */
@keyframes spin{
  to{transform:rotate(360deg);}
}

@keyframes load{
  to{width:100%;}
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
  from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);}
  to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

  <div class="logo">CampusMarket</div>

  <h1>Preparando sua experiência 🚀</h1>

  <p>
    Em instantes você poderá <strong>comprar lanches incríveis</strong>  
    ou começar a <strong>ganhar dinheiro no campus</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="loader"></div>

  <div class="progress">
    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  // redireciona após 2.5s
  setTimeout(() => {
    window.location.href = "/login";
  }, 2500);
</script>

</body>
</html>